[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0019","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0287","title":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook rguest.exe 任意文件访问漏洞","description":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook 0.1 的 rguest.exe CGI 程序存在任意文件访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制请求，利用路径遍历技术读取 Web 服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Guestbook 0.1 版本，攻击条件低、利用简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0287"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.593","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 CGI 目录中删除或重命名 rguest.exe 和 wguest.exe 文件，彻底禁用该留言本组件。在 IIS 中可通过「应用程序配置」移除该脚本映射，或在文件系统层面撤销 IUSR_MACHINENAME 账户对 CGI 目录的执行权限。建议替换为其他仍在维护的开源留言本或使用无文件写入的第三方评论服务（如 Disqus）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92368828704896&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0287","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0132","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0468","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 Microsoft Scriptlet 组件存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用该组件绕过浏览器安全限制，读取客户端文件系统中的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上安装的 IE 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级高，可能导致敏感信息（如本地文件内容）被窃取。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0468"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.557","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-012 提供的 MSHTML.DLL 更新补丁，将 Internet Explorer 升级至已修复版本。该补丁通过更新 MSHTML 解析引擎阻止恶意脚本自动粘贴文件名到文件上传控件，防止文件被未经用户确认即提交至远程服务器。如无法安装补丁，可禁用 ActiveX 控件和脚本功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0468","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/3df4338205b90ec907c1a337dd4fb689267150e3/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0468.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qx62-xr98-6mvc/GHSA-qx62-xr98-6mvc.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c11e9e7e-dc7b-4919-ae86-b7ac71c65565.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000602.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0132.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0134","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0134.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0470","title":"Novell Netware Remote.NLM 弱加密漏洞","description":"Novell Netware 4.1 及 4.11 版本中 Remote.NLM 组件使用弱加密算法对用户密码进行加密处理，攻击者可通过网络嗅探或截获认证数据包后，利用该弱加密算法的可逆性轻易解密出明文密码，从而获得系统未授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 Novell Netware 4.1/4.11 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0470"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.980","remediation":"升级到 Novell NetWare 5.1 及以上版本（SP6 或更高补丁包），其中已使用更强加密算法替代 Remote.NLM 的弱加密。对于已停止支持的版本（NetWare 4.x），建议迁移至 SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 或 Micro Focus Open Enterprise Server 等现代平台，并禁用未加密的远程管理服务（如 Remote.NLM）以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/482","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19364","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0470.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0470","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0470.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0470.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rr53-vc42-qhx6/GHSA-rr53-vc42-qhx6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0470.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f7322e0d-34c4-49a4-86f9-c1810a42d414.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0134.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0137","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0137.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0471","title":"Tiny Software Winroute 远程代理服务器未授权访问漏洞","description":"Winroute 远程代理服务器存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过点击代理配置界面中的 \"cancel\" 按钮，绕过认证机制重新配置代理服务器设置。攻击者可利用此漏洞修改代理规则、劫持网络流量或实施中间人攻击。该漏洞影响 Winroute 代理服务，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，建议用户升级至修复版本或限制对代理管理端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0471"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.113","remediation":"升级到 WinRoute Pro 3.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了远程代理管理接口的未认证访问问题。如无法升级，应在防火墙规则中限制对代理管理端口（默认 3128）的访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 地址连接。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Kerio Control 或其他受支持的防火墙产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0471"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0137.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0801","title":"BMC Patrol 远程攻击者访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"BMC PATROL 4.4 及更早版本的 PATROL Agent 在 TCP 端口 3181 上监听并接收管理控制台发来的管理帧，但其在处理部分管理协议帧时未对来源身份进行充分的认证校验，导致远程攻击者可在未提供有效凭据的情况下伪造控制帧与 Agent 建立会话，从而绕过访问控制机制，执行任意代理操作、读取主机监控信息或下发恶意指令，造成敏感信息泄露与主机被非授权管理的严重后果。攻击仅需网络可达 Agent 端口即可发起，无需本地访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0801"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.163","remediation":"升级 BMC PATROL 至官方修复版本（4.5.00 及以上），在管理控制台启用代理认证与访问控制列表（ACL），禁止未授权主机连接 PATROL Agent 端口（默认 3181/TCP），并在网络边界防火墙限制仅允许受信任管理网段访问 Agent，以缓解远程伪造帧绕过认证的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/2075.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/10323cb4135457b41074412d623aa2116c4e1200/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0801.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0801.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0801.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0801.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1040","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1323","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus NAVIEG及NAVMSE 管理员密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Norton AntiVirus for Internet Email Gateways (NAVIEG) 1.0.1.7及之前版本与Norton AntiVirus for MS Exchange (NAVMSE) 1.5及之前版本存在敏感信息明文存储漏洞。管理员密码以明文形式存储于NAVIEG的navieg.ini配置文件中以及NAVMSE的ModifyPassword注册表项中。本地攻击者可通过读取上述文件或注册表项获取管理员密码，进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响范围较广，利用条件低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1323"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.737","remediation":"立即升级 NAVIEG 至 1.0.1.8 或更高版本，升级 NAVMSE 至 1.6 或更高版本。如无法升级，手动设置 navieg.ini 文件 NTFS 权限为仅管理员可读，并通过注册表编辑器将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Symantec\\NAVMSE\\ModifyPassword 项的权限限制为仅管理员可访问，防止非授权用户读取明文密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92370067416739&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84469/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0138","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0472","title":"NetApp NetCache SNMP 默认团体名安全绕过漏洞","description":"NetApp C630 Netcache 设备中存在 SNMP 默认团体字符串安全配置漏洞。管理员尝试禁用默认的 \"public\" 团体字符串后，该字符串仍未被正确移除，导致攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议利用默认团体字符串远程访问设备，获取系统敏感信息。该漏洞影响 NetApp C630 Netcache 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议管理员手动确认并彻底删除默认团体字符串配置。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0472"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.237","remediation":"立即检查 NetApp NetCache C630 设备上的 SNMP 配置，确认默认 community string \"public\" 是否已被禁用或修改为自定义复杂字符串。由于该产品已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议在设备 ACL 中限制 SNMP（UDP 161/162）仅允许受信任管理 IP 访问，或直接禁用 SNMP 服务。对于仍在运行的旧设备，应尽快迁移至受支持的替代产品。在 Brocade 等后续受影响产品中，升级至厂商确认不受影响的固件版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0472","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0139","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0473","title":"Rsync rsync 目录权限非预期修改漏洞","description":"rsync 2.3.1 之前版本存在权限处理缺陷，在文件传输过程中服务端目录权限可能被错误地应用到客户端工作目录。攻击者可通过构造特定权限的共享目录，诱使客户端执行 rsync 同步操作后，导致客户端工作目录的权限被非预期修改，可能造成信息泄露或权限提升。该漏洞影响广泛使用的 rsync 工具各早期版本，建议升级至 2.3.1 及以上版本修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0473"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.367","remediation":"升级 rsync 至 2.3.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了同步过程中权限被意外修改的问题。如无法升级，避免在不受信任的目录上执行 rsync 拉取操作，并在传输后手动检查并重置工作目录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/145"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1007","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1196","title":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0（一款运行于 Windows 平台的 X Window 服务器软件）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的 6000 端口发送特制的畸形数据包，触发服务进程崩溃或无法正常响应，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Hummingbird Exceed X version 5，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1196"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.377","remediation":"升级至 Hummingbird Exceed 6.0.1、6.0.2 或 6.1 及以上版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。由于 Exceed 5.0 已停止维护，若仍在使用建议迁移至现代 X 服务器替代方案。临时缓解措施：在网络防火墙上封禁 TCP 端口 6000，限制仅受信任的 IP 地址可访问 X11 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13451","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/158","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1196","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1196.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5783344e7c4adc3f449b78e346f760d75b095a9c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/random_crap_DoS.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000601.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--42baa4ee-b6bc-4f5a-9835-e12a18e09f85.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1245","title":"UCD-SNMP SNMP 服务器信息泄露漏洞","description":"ucd-snmp SNMP 服务器 3.52 版本的 vacm 模块未能正确禁用对默认 public 团体字符串的访问权限，导致远程未认证攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议查询目标系统上的敏感系统信息，如系统配置、网络接口状态及运行进程等。该漏洞影响 ucd-snmp 3.52 版本，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1245"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.670","remediation":"升级 ucd-snmp 至 4.0.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Net-SNMP 5.x。同时修改 SNMP 默认 community 字符串，替换 \"public\"/\"private\" 为强密码，并配置 SNMPv3 使用加密认证。在防火墙层面限制 SNMP (UDP 161/162) 仅允许可信管理源 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2086","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1245","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1245.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpj3-2577-2q59/GHSA-fpj3-2577-2q59.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000598.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0112","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0439","title":"Procmail procmailrc 配置文件扩展缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"procmail 3.12 之前版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地或远程攻击者可通过在 procmailrc 配置文件中精心构造恶意的扩展变量，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 procmail 的各类 Linux 发行版（包括 Caldera OpenLinux），CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0439"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.947","remediation":"升级 procmail 至 3.12 及以上版本，该版本已修复 procmailrc 配置文件中扩展处理的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法升级，避免在 procmailrc 中使用不可信来源的变量扩展，并严格限制普通用户修改 procmailrc 配置文件的权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0439","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0439.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0439","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0439.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0439.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vm64-4p36-f6c5/GHSA-vm64-4p36-f6c5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0439.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83086/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990422.data","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6d33fc5b-40ca-4fae-9ac1-3513777b0ab7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0140","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0140.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0474","title":"ICQ ICQ Webserver 目录遍历漏洞","description":"ICQ Webserver 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向服务器发送包含 `../` 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制访问用户个人目录之外的任意文件，导致系统敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 ICQ 版本，攻击条件简单，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0474"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.487","remediation":"立即升级 ICQ 至 99a 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历漏洞。如无法升级，请在 ICQ 设置中禁用内置 Web 服务器功能（Disable ICQ Web Server），并在防火墙层面阻止外部对 ICQ 默认 Web 端口（如 2000/tcp）的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0474"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0140.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0142","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0142.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0475","title":"Procmail .procmailrc 条件竞争任意文件读取漏洞","description":"procmail 在处理 .procmailrc 文件时存在条件竞争漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞读取目标系统上运行 procmail 用户权限可访问的任意文件。该漏洞源于 .procmailrc 文件在处理过程中的检查与使用之间存在时间窗口，攻击者可通过符号链接攻击等方式利用此时间差绕过访问控制，实现任意文件读取。此漏洞影响 procmail 各版本，攻击者需具备本地账户权限，利用条件较低但危害较大，可导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0475"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.627","remediation":"升级 procmail 至 3.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了 .procmailrc 处理过程中的条件竞争漏洞。procmail 已停止维护，建议迁移至 maildrop 作为替代方案。无法升级时，限制 procmail 可执行文件的属组权限，仅允许受信任用户执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0475"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0142.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0122","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0122.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0445","title":"Cisco IOS 12.0 NAT 输入访问列表过滤绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 12.0 版本运行 NAT（网络地址转换）功能时存在访问控制列表绕过漏洞。由于 NAT 处理数据包的顺序问题，部分本应被入站访问控制列表（ACL）过滤的恶意数据包可能绕过 ACL 检查直接进入内部网络，导致 ACL 安全策略失效。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞绕过访问控制，向受保护网络发送未授权流量。该漏洞影响运行 IOS 12.0 并启用 NAT 功能的 Cisco 路由器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0445"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.720","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.0(7) 或更高版本，该版本修复了 NAT 环境下入站访问列表过滤绕过的问题。如无法立即升级，可在入站接口上配置 ip access-group 并启用 ip inspect 或 CBAC 作为临时缓解措施，同时避免在 NAT 接口上依赖纯入站 ACL 过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1104"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0122.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0124","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0124.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0447","title":"HP MPE/iX Debug 工具本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP MPE/iX 操作系统中的调试工具存在权限管理缺陷，本地普通用户可通过使用该调试程序中的 debug 功能获取系统特权，从而实现对系统的完全控制。该漏洞影响 MPE/iX 系列操作系统版本，利用条件要求攻击者拥有本地用户访问权限，在多用户环境下可导致敏感信息泄露与系统完整性破坏。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0447"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.963","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBMP9904-006 提供的 MPE/iX 调试工具修补补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应从用户账户中移除 DEBUG 能力（capability），或删除非必要系统上的 DEBUG/PATCH 文件系统，限制仅管理员可访问调试工具，防止本地用户利用调试工具提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBMP9904-006"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0124.toml"}]